msgid ":tagdef:`[SuperWeapon]Cursor=mouse cursor`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/superweapons/types/empulse.rst:38
msgid "Used when the target is in range of a cannon. Defaults to :value:`Attack`."
msgstr ""

